snippet.title: Tokyo Dark | Release Date Reveal Trailer | Square Enix Collective | ESRB
snippet.description:
There is an urban legend in Japan that, deep below the sewers of Tokyo, there is a door. 
All who enter are lost forever...

Tokyo Dark is coming to PC on September 7th!
